originalText.text: I have been a client of Alicia's for ten years now; I followed her from San Francisco to New York. Everyone knows that she is the best massage therapist in NYC, but her true secret weapon is acupuncture. Her treatments are out of this world - she is with you the entire time and exudes knowledge, wisdom, compassion and healing. I have been to my fair share of acupuncturists over the years, but no one seems to understand my damp spleen like Alicia! Her treatments are incredibly effective and her herbal medicine skills are just beyond. I feel energized, relaxed and whole after each session with her. Give your constitution a treat & book a treatment with her.

originalText.text: Alicia is the best massage therapist I have ever worked with (and I am a massage addict with chronic jaw & neck pain). I have been getting massages with her regularly for twelve years now and I feel that working with her has made a huge difference in my health, attitude and well being. She is amazing!! She does the best deep tissue work, but also is incredibly supportive, nurturing and every massage is unique. I highly recommend visiting her - your body will thank you!!  Also, she is an amazing acupuncturist & her combination massage & acupuncture sessions will heal just about anything. I also have a chronic health condition & Alicia's sessions and herbs, in addition to massage, are the only thing that has healed me. Thank you, Alicia!
